  tradePageUrl="/structural-steelworkers/ai-receptionist/"
  ctaHeadline="Recover Five Steelwork Leads from One February Mezzanine Friday"
  ctaSubhead={`While your crew bolted the mezzanine secondaries, five callers missed you. Five texts went out. Five replied. A warehouse frame, paired RSJs, an exposed canopy, rusted purlins, and a loading bay. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
